<P>
DIGEST / LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF: GANG MEMBER ARRESTED IN LANCASTER STABBING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A California City man has been arrested in the stabbing of a 17-year-old 
Lancaster youth, who was allegedly attacked last week by four gang members 
after refusing to tell them what school he attended. 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles County sheriff's deputies from the gang detail of the Antelope 
