Show-Ya's attempt to capture U.S. market. ; Photo, (Orange County Edition) Lead 
singer Keiko Terada of Show-Ya, all-female Japanese hard-rock quintet, during 
concert at the Palace in Hollywood on Wednesday. ROBERT GABRIEL / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Keiko Terada: solid voice behind a doll-like exterior. 
</P>
