HUSSEINI, FAISAL; ARRESTS; CIVIL DISOBEDIENCE; MIDDLE EAST PEACE; UNITED STATES 
-- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; EGYPT -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- ISRAEL 
</P>
