CALIFORNIA; GOVERNMENT MISCONDUCT; CALIFORNIA -- CONSTITUTIONS; MEDICAL CARE -- 
STATE AID; SEPARATION OF POWERS; CALIFORNIA -- SUITS; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- 
