ABUSE; CHILD MOLESTATION; CIVIL RIGHTS VIOLATIONS; SUITS; TRIALS; LIABILITY 
INSURANCE; INSURANCE INDUSTRY; KABC (TELEVISION STATION); SATZ, WAYNE 
</P>
